President John Magufuli has instructed the contractor in charge of the Arusha water project to complete the project by the end of December this year. Dr Magufuli said this on Friday this week while in Arusha, where he instructed the contractor to work hard and ensure the project is complete on time. Elaborating, President Magufuli said when the project is complete; it will be able to supply more water than the required amount needed by the residents. He mentioned the areas where the project will cover to include neighboring districts of Hai, Simanjiro and Arumaru.